<li>The bot WILL get questions wrong at first - it learns as it completes your homework.</li>
<li>If nothing is happening, try refreshing the page.</li>
<li>The bot will try to answer drag-and-drop questions, but there might be errors that require you to solve the questions on your own.</li>
<li>Make sure you are completing SmartBook 2.0 assignments. The bot will not work with other McGrawHill assessments.</li>
<li>If the URL isn't "learning.mheducation.com", the bot may not work.</li>
<li>Having a poor internet connection may cause the bot to run into errors.</li>
<li>If the issue persists, please let us know with the anonymous form below.</li>
